name: SimpleSocial
author: Bryan Hadaway

sections.description:
Display icons for your social media profile links.

Icons are set under Appearance > Menus.

  • Simply create a custom menu, add custom links to it, add the desired platform name to each link’s respective Navigation Label (Facebook, Twitter, etc.), assign the menu to the SimpleSocial location, and use the shortcode [simplesocial] in any Page, Post, or Text Widget
  • You can drag and drop icon menu items in any order you like (just like any normal WordPress menu)
  • You can set the universal icon size and color under Settings > SimpleSocial

Icons by Simple Icons | Plugin by Bryan Hadaway

Supported icons:

  • Facebook
  • X/Twitter
  • Instagram
  • TikTok
  • LinkedIn
  • YouTube
  • Pinterest

1500+ more in the pro version.

short_description: Display icons for your social media profile links.
description:
Display icons for your social media profile links.

Icons are set under Appearance > Menus.

  • Simply create a custom menu, add custom links to it, add the desired platform name to each link’s respective Navigation Label (Facebook, Twitter, etc.), assign the menu to the SimpleSocial location, and use the shortcode [simplesocial] in any Page, Post, or Text Widget
  • You can drag and drop icon menu items in any order you like (just like any normal WordPress menu)
  • You can set the universal icon size and color under Settings > SimpleSocial

Icons by Simple Icons | Plugin by Bryan Hadaway

Supported icons:

  • Facebook
  • X/Twitter
  • Instagram
  • TikTok
  • LinkedIn
  • YouTube
  • Pinterest

1500+ more in the pro version.
